Joh 13:17 εἰ ταῦτα <span class='verb'>οἴδατε</span> <span class='punctuation'>,</span> μακάριοί <span class='verb'>ἐστε</span> ἐὰν <span class='verb'>ποιῆτε</span> αὐτά <span class='punctuation'>.</span>【你們既知道這事，若是去行就有福了。】<span class='paragraph'></span>
